high_descs: Move to the table to the left of you
pick up the lettuce from the table
move to the fridge behind you
chill the lettuce in the fridge
move to the sink to the left of you
put the lettuce in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a head of chilled lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the brown table that is now to your right.
Pick up the piece of lettuce that is on the table.
Turn around and walk over to the refrigerator.
Cool off the piece of lettuce in the fridge before pulling it back out.
Turn to the left and walk over to the marble kitchen sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink to the left of the other items.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled piece of lettuce into the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Move the table behind you across from the sink.
Pick up the lettuce from the table.
Move to the fridge behind you.
Place the lettuce inside and chill for a moment before retrieving and closing the door.
Move to the sink to the left of you.
Place the lettuce inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce from the table in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the table.
Pick up the lettuce from the table.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Put the lettuce in the refrigerator and take the lettuce out of the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the sink
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, move forward, turn right to face the table.
Pick up the lettuce on the table.
Turn around, bring the lettuce to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge.
Bring the the chilled lettuce to the left and back to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce in the sink.
